Some MCQS on if-else statement

1. An if-esle statement is also called
A. Boolean  B. Control Statements  C. Both 

2. Java styles if-else statments is also called as 
A. C  B. C++  C. Both

3. Every if Statement is followed by else or else if statement
a. True  B. False  C. None of them


4. An if statement code must be defined in two braces
A. False  B. True  C. None of them

5. What is the output of the following.
if(true)
{
    break;
    System.out.println("Elephant");
}
A. It gives the output Elephant
B. Compile Time error
C. None of them
